showHexGrid.hint:
{View Hex Grid}

Displays a hex grid over the battlefield.
(hotkey - F6)

movementShadow.hint:
{Movement Shadow}

Displays a shadow on the battlefield which shows where a unit can currently move to.
(hotkey - F8)

cursorShadow.hint:
{Cursor Shadow}

Places a hex shadow under the mouse cursor.
(hotkey - F7)

allStatistics.hint:
{All Statistics}

Right clicking on a unit will display all statistics about the unit, including any spells that are currently in effect.
(hotkey - F5)

onlySpells.hint:
{Spells Only}

Right clicking on a unit will only display any spells that are currently affecting the unit.
(hotkey - F5)

menu.hint:
{Main Menu}

Abandon game and return to the main menu.
(hotkey on adventure map - Esc; in the options window - M)

load.hint:
{Load Game}

Load a saved game.
(hotkey - L)

save.hint:
{Save Game}

СSave the current game.
(hotkey - S)

restart.hint:
{Restart Scenario}

Restart the current scenario
(hotkey on adventure map - N - return to "New Game" menu; in the options window - R - restarting this scenario)

return.hint:
{Return to Game}

Return to the last window.
(hotkey in the options window - Esc/Enter)
